@node "Obsolete Commands"

There are a few TurboText commands from previous versions which have been
replaced with more flexible and superior alternatives. These are:

@{" SizeWindow " link "SizeWindow"} and @{" MoveWindow " link "MoveWindow"} are replaced with @{" MoveSizeWindow " link "MoveSizeWindow"} which
is faster and more reliable.

The @{b}WindowPos@{ub} and @{b}WindowSize@{ub} options to the @{" SetPrefs " link "SetPrefs"} command are
replaced by the @{b}WINDOW@{ub} parameter to the @{" OpenDoc " link "OpenDoc"} command.

