@endnode


@node "HelpNode"
@title "Help"

Format:		Help <topic>

Template:	FILE/K,TOPIC

Release:	Version 1.0

Purpose: 
Start an AmigaGuide window showing information on the requested topic.

Specifications: 
Help opens up an AmigaGuide window showing information on the topic
requested. If no topic is specified, then the main node of the AmigaGuide
document is displayed.

The FILE parameter lets you specify the name of an AmigaGuide file to
load. If this parameter is not supplied, then the TurboText manual is
automatically used.

If no FILE and no TOPIC parameters are given, then the TurboText manual is
loaded, and its table of contents is displayed.

