@node "HideFold"

Format:		HideFold [NESTED | ALL]

Template:	NESTED/S,ALL/S

Release:	Version 1.0

Purpose: 
Remake folds.

Specifications: 
HideFold remakes @{" folds " link "Folds"} having been revealed by @{" ShowFold " link "ShowFold"}. Invoked by
itself, this command hides the fold currently under the cursor only. When
provided the NESTED option all folds within the current fold are also
hidden. When passed the ALL option, all folds within the current document
are hidden.

See Also: @{" MakeFold   " link "MakeFold"}
