@node "IconifyWindow"

Format:		IconifyWindow [ON | OFF | TOGGLE]

Template:	ON/S,OFF/S,TOGGLE/S

Release:	Version 1.0

Purpose: 
Iconify or de-iconify a document window.

Specifications: 
IconifyWindow changes the iconified state of the current
@{" document window " link "The TurboText Document Window"}. Invoked with the ON option, this command iconifies the
document window if it is not already iconified. Invoked with the OFF
option, this command deiconifies the document window if it was iconified.
Finally, if invoked with the TOGGLE option, this command changes the state
of the document window from iconified to deiconified, or vice-versa.

