@node "Insert"

Format:		Insert <text>

Template:	TEXT/F

Release:	Version 1.0

Purpose: 
Insert characters within the current document at the current cursor
position.

Specifications: 
This command inserts characters in the current document, taking into
account embedded linefeeds, the current @{" right margin " link "Preferences - Editing"}, @{" word wrap " link "Editing Modes"} and
@{" auto-indent " link "Editing Modes"}. The single parameter specifies the characters to insert.
This command behaves exactly like inserting text manually in the document.

