@node "InsertFile"

Format:		InsertFile [filename]

Template:	NAME/F

Release:	Version 2.0

Purpose: 
Insert a file from disk at the current cursor position in the document.

Specifications: 
InsertFile inserts the contents of a file on disk in the current document,
at the current cursor position.

An optional filename may be specified. If the filename is present, the
editor attempts to insert that file from disk. If the filename is not
present, then the @{" file requester " link "The File Requester"} is opened allowing the user to select a
file. Note that when a filename is specified, it must be fully qualified
(i.e. have a complete directory path).

