@node "InsertLine"

Format:		InsertLine [NOBREAK] [INDENT]

Template:	NOBREAK/S,INDENT/S

Release:	Version 1.0

Purpose: 
Insert a linefeed at the current cursor position.

Specifications: 
InsertLine inserts a single linefeed character at the current cursor
position. This has the same effect as pressing @{b}[Return]@{ub} within a document.
The NOBREAK option causes a new line to be inserted after the current line,
without breaking the current line. The INDENT option overrides the current
setting of auto-indent mode and indents the new line.

See Also: @{" DeleteLine " link "DeleteLine"}
