@endnode


@node "MakeFold"

Format:		MakeFold

Template:	,

Release:	Version 1.0

Purpose: 
Create a fold with the currently selected block, or using indentation
level at the current cursor position.

Specifications: 
MakeFold creates a @{" fold " link "Folds"} within the current document. If there is
currently a @{" selected block " link "Selection Blocks"}, it is folded away. If there is currently no
selected block, the fold is created by looking at the current indentation
level and folding every line which follows the current line and has a
greater indentation level, until a line with equal or lower indentation
level is encountered.

See Also: @{" HideFold   " link "HideFold"}
