Template:	FOLDS/S,LINE/N,COLUMN/N

Release:	Version 1.0

Purpose: 
Move the cursor to a specific line and column within the current document.

Specifications: 
This command moves the cursor to a specific line and column within the
current document. The first numeric parameter specifies the line, the
second specifies the column. If the line parameter is not provided, a
