The single parameter specifies the number of the bookmark to go to. The
bookmark must have been previously set by the SetBookmark command. An
implicit @{" CenterView " link "CenterView"} command is executed whenever the cursor is moved to
a bookmark. This does not happen with bookmark 0 however which is meant
