			RightMargin <right margin> |
			SaveIcons [ON | OFF | TOGGLE] |
			SaveEOLAs <0=LF, 1=CR, 2=CRLF>
			ScreenMode <graphics database mode id> |
			ScreenName <public screen name> |
			ScreenSize <screen width height> |
			ScrollGadget <0=right, 1=left, 0=none> |
			SelectWhenDragging [ON | OFF | TOGGLE] |
			ShowEOF [ON | OFF | TOGGLE] |
			ShowEOLS [ON | OFF | TOGGLE] |
			ShowSpaces [ON | OFF | TOGGLE] |
